# Code Standards

## JavaScript
- Use ES6+ features, British English spelling
- Meaningful variable/function names, JSDoc for complex functions
- Prefer const over let, avoid var

## CSS
- Kebab-case class names, semantic naming
- Group related styles, use CSS custom properties
- Mobile-first responsive design

## HTML
- Semantic elements, proper accessibility attributes
- Clean minimal markup, descriptive alt text
